commit 877fe816a75030c5e82b1b1b72398033011afbec
Author: Emmanuele Bassi <ebassi@gnome.org>
Date:   Mon Feb 13 09:33:19 2017 +0000

    Allow using Python3 to run gen_dispatch.py
    
