Date:   Wed Dec 7 15:12:15 2016 +0000

    Avoid C99 declaration after statement
    
    The rest of the library is C89-only, so we should keep it that way.

 src/dispatch_common.c | 5 +++--
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

